'''圣多明我广场'''（Piazza San Domenico）是[[意大利|意大利]]南部[[西西里大区|西西里大区]][[巴勒莫|巴勒莫]]的一个广场。它位于巴勒莫历史中心的洛吉亚区（La Loggia）的[[罗马街_(巴勒莫)|罗马街]]（Via Roma）旁。广场的名字来源于该市的著名景点之一[[圣多明我堂_(巴勒莫)|圣多明我堂]]（San Domenico）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.it/books?id=XtEJDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA183&dq=piazza+san+domenico+column+palermo&hl=it&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi-sP2w0eXUAhUKfhoKHcrwACwQ6AEIIzAA#v=onepage&q=piazza%20san%20domenico%20column%20palermo&f=false |title=Dummett J., ''Palermo, City of Kings: The Heart of Sicily'', I.B.Tauris, 2015, p. 183. |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2018-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718174501/https://books.google.it/books?id=XtEJDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA183&dq=piazza+san+domenico+column+palermo&hl=it&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi-sP2w0eXUAhUKfhoKHcrwACwQ6AEIIzAA#v=onepage&q=piazza%20san%20domenico%20column%20palermo&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。过去，它被称为帝国广场（"''Piazza Imperiale''"），因为它是由[[查理六世_(神圣罗马帝国)|查理六世]]皇帝决定开辟的<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.it/books?id=WI8j4eAz1LsC&pg=PA255&dq=piazza+san+domenico+palermo&hl=it&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi2v4rTzuXUAhXFORoKHSByCeMQ6AEIKzAB#v=onepage&q=piazza%20san%20domenico%20palermo&f=false |title=Ciccarelli D., Valenza M.D., ''La Sicilia e l'Immacolata: non solo 150 anni : atti del convegno di studio, Palermo, 1-4 dicembre 2004'', Officina di Studi Medievali, 2006, p. 255. |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2018-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718174730/https://books.google.it/books?id=WI8j4eAz1LsC&pg=PA255&dq=piazza+san+domenico+palermo&hl=it&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi2v4rTzuXUAhXFORoKHSByCeMQ6AEIKzAB#v=onepage&q=piazza%20san%20domenico%20palermo&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

广场的中间矗立着无玷始胎柱（Colonna dell'Immacolata）,由托马索·那波利（Tommaso Napoli）于1724年设计，1728年由乔瓦尼·比亚吉奥·阿米科（Giovanni Biagio Amico）建造。俯瞰广场的原[[多明我会|多明我会]]修道院是复兴运动博物馆（Museo del Risorgimento）的位置。此外，广场也是古老的武契里亚（Vucciria）市场的入口。

